1. Create feedback mechanism loop infrastructure
1a. Disable version control branching in the codebase
1b. Whenever the change is pushed to master it should trigger the feedback process
1c. When the feedback constrains are met only then the change should land in master branch
1d. The constraints are , all the tests should pass , coding conventions are followed and change size is below some threshold
1e. Decouple release from deployment and control release through feature toggles
1f. Notify on slack the status of the feedback process along with the url and version number.